</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-30_ pf-text-1"><strong>Professional development</strong> - Continuous education and training to enhance an individual's skills and knowledge, ensuring they remain competent in their profession.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-32_ pf-text-1"><strong>Compliance</strong> - Adherence to laws, regulations, guidelines, and specifications relevant to an organisation's business processes.






